        <title>Manage volumes</title>
        <paragraph>Depending on the setup of your cloud provider, they may give you an endpoint to
            use to manage volumes, or there may be an extension under the covers. In either
            case, you can use the <literal>openstack</literal> CLI to manage volumes.</paragraph>
